DATA PRIVACY NOTE:
This software is designed to be self-hosted. No data is transmitted to external
services by the application itself, EXCEPT for user-configured AI providers
(Bring Your Own API key). Data flow to AI providers is governed by the user's
own agreement with the AI provider. The application authors are not responsible
for data handling by third-party AI services.

By using this software with AI features enabled, you acknowledge that your
DRP content (sections, BIA data, etc.) may be sent to the AI provider you
configured, subject to that provider's data policy.
